short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Catalysi extension to connect with LinkedIn

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension securely connects to a user's LinkedIn profile to gather additional information, enabling deeper analysis and insights based on the user's LinkedIn data. It will store data only if a user gives consent.
